<Layout title="Bitcoin Halving Explained: What It Is and Why It Matters" description="Understand Bitcoin halving — what happens every 210,000 blocks, how it affects supply and price, and why miners and investors watch it closely." keywords="bitcoin halving, btc halving explained, bitcoin halving 2024, block reward, bitcoin mining reward, crypto halving, bitcoin supply schedule">
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
